Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 军部来不及追击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护卡嘉莉小姐
