Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom?
